# Comprehensive Markdown to HTML Parser Module (Facade)
# Pure Simple implementation - NO generics, NO try/catch, NO chained methods
# Tuple-based AST, supports CommonMark + GFM features

# Module Organization:
# - types.spl: AST structure definitions (tuple-based)
# - utilities.spl: Character/string utilities, HTML escaping, slugification, line processing (29 functions)
# - block.spl: Block-level pattern detection (19 functions)
# - inline.spl: Inline parsing helpers and token parsing (14 functions)
# - parse.spl: Block parsing (8 functions)
# - render.spl: HTML rendering (12 functions + 6 public API functions)

# Public API:
# - markdown_to_html(markdown: text) -> text
# - markdown_to_ast(markdown: text) -> array
# - extract_headings(blocks: array) -> array
# - extract_links(blocks: array) -> array

